headline: Trump Is Winning the Fight Against Offshore Wind Despite Court Losses
summary: “The courts can stop the abrupt enforcement of policies, but they can’t really restart a stable pipeline for these projects,” said Atin Jain, an analyst at BloombergNEF.  “Under this kind of policy environment, nobody is going to touch US offshore wind for some time.”
